company,	1
nor	1
even	1
by	1
the	1
praises	1
of	1
her	1
godmother,	1
who,	1
for	1
the	1
purpose	1
of	1
condoling	1
with	1
her,	1
said,	1
"Well,	1
my	1
dear	1
Rosamond,	1
I	1
admire	1
your	1
generous	1
spirit.	1
You	1
know	1
I	1
prophesied	1
that	1
your	1
half-guinea	1
would	1
be	1
gone	1
the	1
soonest.	1
Did	1
I	1
not,	1
Laura?"	1
said	1
she,	1
appealing,	1
in	1
a	1
sarcastic	1
tone,	1
to	1
where	1
she	1
thought	1
Laura	1
was.	1
"Where	1
is	1
Laura?	1
I	1
don't	1
see	1
her."	1
Laura	1
came	1
forward.	1
"You	1
are	1
too	1
PRUDENT	1
to	1
throw	1
away	1
your	1
money	1
like	1
your	1
sister.	1
Your	1
half-guinea,	1
I'll	1
answer	1
for	1
it,	1
is	1
snug	1
in	1
your	1
pocket--Is	1
it	1
not?"	1
"No,	1
madam,"	1
answered	1
she,	1
in	1
a	1
low	1
voice.	1
But	1
low	1
as	1
the	1
voice	1
of	1
Laura	1
was,	1
the	1
poor	1
little	1
lace-girl	1
heard	1
it;	1
and	1
now,	1
for	1
the	1
first	1
time,	1
fixing	1
her	1
eyes	1
upon	1
Laura,	1
recollected	1
her	1
benefactress.	1
"Oh,	1
that's	1
the	1
young	1
lady!"	1
she	1
exclaimed,	1
in	1
a	1
tone	1
of	1
joyful	1
gratitude,	1
"the	1
good,	1
good	1
young	1
lady,	1
who	1
gave	1
me	1
the	1
half-	1
guinea,	1
and	1
would	1
not	1
stay	1
to	1
be	1
thanked	1
for	1
it;	1
but	1
I	1
WILL	1
thank	1
her	1
now."	1
"The	1
half-guinea,	1
Laura!"	1
said	1
her	1
godmother.	1
"What	1
is	1
all	1
this?"	1
"I'll	1
tell	1
you,	1
madam,	1
if	1
you	1
please,"	1
said	1
the	1
little	1
girl.	1
It	1
was	1
not	1
in	1
expectation	1
of	1
being	1
praised	1
for	1
it,	1
that	1
Laura	1
had	1
been	1
generous,	1
and	1
therefore	1
everybody	1
was	1
really	1
touched	1
with	1
the	1
history	1
of	1
the	1
weaving-pillow;	1
and	1
whilst	1
they	1
praised,	1
felt	1
a	1
certain	1
degree	1
of	1
respect,	1
which	1
is	1
not	1
always	1
felt	1
by	1
those	1
who	1
pour	1
forth	1
eulogiums.	1
RESPECT	1
is	1
not	1
an	1
improper	1
word,	1
even	1
applied	1
to	1
a	1
child	1
of	1
Laura's	1
age;	1
for	1
let	1
the	1
age	1
or	1
situation	1
of	1
the	1
person	1
be	1
what	1
it	1
may,	1
they	1
command	1
respect	1
who	1
deserve	1
it.	1
"Ah,	1
madam!"	1
said	1
Rosamond	1
to	1
her	1
godmother,	1
"now	1
you	1
see--you	1
see	1
